lead_paragraph: Russell Westbrook had 26 points, 12 assists and 11 rebounds in his 16th triple-double of the season, Kevin Durant scored 34 points and the Oklahoma City Thunder beat the Toronto Raptors 119-100 on Monday night for their eighth straight victory.

headline.main: Westbrook's 16th Triple-Double Leads Thunder to 8th in a Row
headline.print_headline: Westbrook's 16th Triple-Double Leads Thunder to 8th in a Row
